#: ../../layers/proprietary.rst:29
msgid ""
"The Bing tiles API requires that you register for an API key to use with "
"your mapping application.  The example here uses an API key that you should "
"not use in production.  To use the Bing layer in production, register for an "
"API key at https://www.bingmapsportal.com/."
